1.0.1.name: wordpress/zeebizzcard
1.0.1.description: zeeBizzCard is a clean and elegant styled Business Card Theme for WordPress that fits perfectly for a sleek homepage for personalities, freelancers, entrepreneurs or small business owners. It comes with a Featured Posts Slider, a custom post types based Portfolio and Shortcodes for Resume, AboutMe Box and Skills. The theme also has an extensive theme options panel where you can change colors, fonts, layouts etc.
